<div class="comment"><div class="commtext c00">For the specific case of solving shell script dependencies, Nix is actually very straightforward. Packaging a script is a writeShellApplication call and calling it is a `nix run`.<p>I guess the issue is just that nobody has documented how to do that one specific thing so you can only learn this technique by trying to learn Nix as a whole.<p>So perhaps the thing you&#x27;re envisaging could just be a wrapper for this Nix logic.</div><div class="reply"><p><font size="1"><u><a href="reply?id=44370757&amp;goto=item%3Fid%3D44369388%2344370757" rel="nofollow">reply</a></u></font></div></div></td></tr>
